@startuml
autonumber
actor "Utility Operator" as Actor

box "Orchestration Layer" #LightCyan
participant "Camunda Engine" as Camunda
participant "Kong Gateway" as Kong
end box

box "Microservice Layer" #LightYellow
participant "Utility Operator MS" as UOMS
end box

box "Data Layer" #LightGreen
database "AWS RDS " as DBu
end box

note over Actor, DBu: Decommissioning/Deregistration process follows the same information flow but using operators like DELETE

== Utility Operator Registration ==
Actor -> Camunda: Operator Register
Camunda -> Kong: POST /UtilityOperator
Kong -> UOMS: Forward Request
UOMS -> DBu: JDBC INSERT INTO UtilityOperator: \n(Name, Location)
DBu --> UOMS: 200 OK
UOMS --> Kong: 201 Created
Kong --> Camunda: 201 Created
Camunda --> Actor: Successful Registration

== Grid Cell Registration ==
Actor -> Camunda: Register Grid Cell
Camunda -> Kong: POST /UtilityOperator/GridCell
Kong -> UOMS: Forward Request
UOMS -> DBu: JDBC INSERT INTO GridCell: \n(GridCellId, UtilityOperatorId, \nMaxCapacity, GeographicBoundaries)
DBu --> UOMS: 200 OK
UOMS --> Kong: 201 Created
Kong --> Camunda: 201 Created
Camunda --> Actor: Grid Cell Successfully Added
@enduml